OL,3,CSenior minister says charities may
OL,4,Cneed to merge to bring down costs
OL,6,FJersey's Deputy Chief Minister is
OL,7,Furging charities to collaborate to
OL,8,Fsave money as donations continue to
OL,9,Fdecline amid the cost of living crisis.
OL,11,FThere are more than 400 non-profit
OL,12,Forganisations on the island and Deputy
OL,13,FTom Binet says there is too much
OL,14,Foverlap with doubling up on
OL,15,Fbureaucracy.
OL,17,FHe explains: "As we move to make
OL,18,Fthings more efficient, I think local
OL,19,Fcharities need to be talking to each
OL,20,Fother more to see if they can
OL,21,Famalgamate.
