OL,3,CSenior minister says charities may
OL,4,Cneed to merge to bring down costs
OL,6,FA third of charities in Jersey already
OL,7,Fshare physical resources but say the
OL,8,Funderlying problem is a decline in
OL,9,Fdonations from the public.
OL,11,FPam Aubert, Chief Executive Officer of
OL,12,FJersey Cancer Trust, explains: "I
OL,13,Fthink we are all living through a
OL,14,Freally difficult time with the cost of
OL,15,Fliving, so to give a donation to a
OL,16,Fcharity is a really valuable thing to
OL,17,Fdo.
