OL,3,CSenior minister says charities may
OL,4,Cneed to merge to bring down costs
OL,6,F"I give monthly to causes close to my
OL,7,Fheart, it allows charities to almost
OL,8,Fforecast for that sustainable income.
OL,9,FIt is great to have events but they
OL,10,Fhappen once a year.
OL,12,F"Whereas a regular gift, like a
OL,13,Fmonthly donation, can really make a
OL,14,Fdifference."
